<div class="row">
  <div class="col-xs-10 col-sm-8 col-md-6 col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-4 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-offset-2 col-xs-offset-1">
    <p>
     <center><div id="notice"><span class="label label-warning"><%= notice %></span></div><div id="alert"><span class="label label-danger"><%= alert %></span></div></center>
    </p>
    <div class="well">
      <%= form_for(@airvm) do |f| %>
        <% if @airvm.errors.any? %>
          <div id="error_explanation">
            <h2><%= pluralize(@airvm.errors.count, "error") %> prohibited this airvm from being saved:</h2>

            <ul>
            <% @airvm.errors.full_messages.each do |message| %>
              <li><%= message %></li>
            <% end %>
            </ul>
          </div>
        <% end %>

        <fieldset>
          <legend>
            <center>
              <img src="<%= asset_path('vcloudairlogo.png') %>" style="width:100px;"> <h3>vCloud Air VMs</h3>
            </center>
          </legend>
          <form class="form-horizontal" role="form">
            <div class="form-group">
              <p>
                <%= f.label "username:", :class => "col-lg-3 col-lg-offset-1 control-label", :style => "text-align: right;" %>
                  <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <%= f.text_field :user, :placeholder => "username@org", :class => "form-control" %></p>                  
                  </div>
              </p>
            </div>
            <br>
            <div class="form-group">
              <p>
                <%= f.label "password:", :class => "col-lg-3 col-lg-offset-1 control-label", :style => "text-align: right;" %>
                  <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <%= f.password_field :password, :placeholder => "password", :autocomplete => "off", :class => "form-control" %>
                  </div>
              </p>
            </div>
            <br>
            <br>
            <div class="form-group">
              <p>
                <%= f.label "host:", :class => "col-lg-3 col-lg-offset-1 control-label", :style => "text-align: right;" %> 
                  <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <%= f.text_field :host, :placeholder => "p0v11-vcd.vchs.vmware.com", :class => "form-control" %>             
                  </div>
              </p>
            </div>
          </form>
          <br>
          <br>

          <center>
            <div class="form-group">  
              <%= f.submit :value => "Login", class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
            </div>
          </center>
            <a href="#" id="infolink"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign" style="float: left;"></span></a>
            <a href="#" id="contactlink"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user" style="float: right;"></span></a>
        </fieldset>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-10 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-offset-3 col-xs-offset-1">
        <div id="info">
          <p>This project will be able to show information about all the virtual machines inside of your vCloud Air Organization. Username and Passwords are stored in 256-bit encryption. AJAX calls done on the site are still unsafe. However, Each login creates a new UUID for the web address. Still pretty damn secure.</p>
          <p>Once you are finished, you can click the "Destroy" button that will destroy your UN/PW/Host entry into the system and will not be able to be recovered. Simple as that! </p>
          <img src="<%= asset_path('ss.png') %>" style="width:100%;">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-10 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-offset-3 col-xs-offset-1">
        <div id="contact">
          <center>
            <p>a project by kendrick coleman</p>
            <%=link_to image_tag("rss_150.png", :width => '45', :padding => '10'), "http://www.kendrickcoleman.com"  %>
            <%=link_to image_tag("twitter_150.png", :width => '45', :padding => '10'), "https://twitter.com/KendrickColeman"  %>
            <%=link_to image_tag("facebook_150.png", :width => '45', :padding => '10'), "https://www.facebook.com/pages/kendrickcolemancom/148077885252956"  %>
            <%=link_to image_tag("github_150.png", :width => '45', :padding => '10'), "https://github.com/kacole2"  %>
          </center>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
$( document ).ready(function() {
    $("#info").hide();
    $("#contact").hide();

    $("#infolink").click(function() {
      $("#info").toggle();
    });

    $("#contactlink").click(function() {
      $("#contact").toggle();
    });

});
</script>
